data.description: Are you looking to be close to all Palm Beach has to offer: beaches, entertainment, fine dining, Spring Training games, golf & ease to travel? This spacious home is located in one of West Palm Beach's premier gated communities. The design is perfect for entertaining or relaxing in newly resurfaced/ heated pool while enjoying the private oversized backyard. The main level features a formal living & dining room, an open kitchen, breakfast & family room overlooking the pool with easy access to the first floor 1/2 bath. The upstairs hosts 4 bedrooms & 3 full baths with the addition a loft area perfect for an in home office. Community amenities include pools, playground, tennis & basketball courts. Be sure to check this out in person & envision all the fun family memories just waiting for you.
